{"tid":1576033,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"撞鐵地點近poly Z core撞鬼隧道","createTime":"2019-09-17T05:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T05:41:49.000Z","uid":151065,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"095b82bd31c918f5aa47cc82d72fba4d09daee5e","tid":1576033,"uid":151065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:18:28.000Z","msg":"Poly係猛鬼校園，仲係八大之最。除咗近殯儀館之外，據說，以前起Z core 時，因為同紅磡校舍分離，所以要起一條隧道去連接兩個校舍。有一晚，工人連夜趕工，開鑿隧道。呢個時候，其中一名工人發現地底有一副骸骨。佢想通知同伴，就聽到把聲話：「救我。」佢嚇到拋低所有工具，即刻逃走。點知，佢喺隧道不停徘徊，明明出口好近，但係點樣都出唔到去。第二日，其他工人發現佢死喺隧道，而屍首同骸骨放置嘅姿勢正正相同，一陣陰風吹過，佢地不約而同地聽到兩把聲：「救我⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以今次單野一定係冥界對黨鐵嘅警告！</span></span>"},{"pid":"09563a42667a6f43161a04a98915add835896640","tid":1576033,"uid":151065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:18:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba82ec68b202c90ab1a12181b842e72754a6ae08","tid":1576033,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72279ff7e936e6e1976fd1a5177a7635e87ad29f","tid":1576033,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:25:10.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/StbtyWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.li